=== 對現實社群的影響 ===
遊戲龐大的玩家人口帶來不少意想不到的正面影響。例如，遊戲讓玩家得以事先阻止或通報犯罪，<ref>{{cite news |title = Pokemon Go Is Helping Both Cops and Robbers Do Their Jobs |url = http://fortune.com/2016/07/14/pokemon-go-robberies-police/ |accessdate = 2016-07-14 |work = Fortune |date = 2016-07-14 |archive-date = 2016-07-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160715143202/http://fortune.com/2016/07/14/pokemon-go-robberies-police/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1 = Daye |first1 = Alison |title = Pokémon Go helps two Marines to catch a murder suspect in Fullerton |url = http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/13/us/pokmon-go-helps-marines-to-catch-suspect/index.html |accessdate = 2016-07-14 |work = CNN |date = 2016-07-13 |archive-date = 2016-07-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160717170356/http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/13/us/pokmon-go-helps-marines-to-catch-suspect/index.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1 = Reports |first1 = Staff |title = Four arrested after robbery in Auburn connected to 'Pokémon Go' app |url = http://www.oanow.com/news/crime_courts/four-arrested-after-robbery-in-auburn-connected-to-pok-mon/article_4e7e5e5e-492c-11e6-94d7-5fc7b8837e8d.html |accessdate = 2016-07-14 |date = 2016-07-13 |archive-date = 2022-03-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220319102122/https://oanow.com/news/crime_courts/four-arrested-after-robbery-in-auburn-connected-to-pok-mon/article_4e7e5e5e-492c-11e6-94d7-5fc7b8837e8d.html }}</ref><ref name="Kuna, Idaho Arson">{{cite web |url = http://www.idahostatesman.com/news/local/crime/article88912227.html |title = Pokemon Go players tip Kuna police to alleged arson near church |publisher = The Idaho Statesman |date = 2016-07-11 |accessdate = 2016-07-14 }}</ref>甚至可以一定程度上加強社區居民與執法單位間的關係，<ref name="Community relations.">{{cite web | url=https://finance.yahoo.com/news/pokemon-blamed-crimes-aids-embattled-004344471.html | title=Pokemon Go blamed for crimes but also aids embattled U.S. police | publisher=Forbes | date=2016-07-13 | accessdate=2016-07-16 | author=Cherelus, Gina | archive-date=2016-08-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814162627/http://finance.yahoo.com/news/pokemon-blamed-crimes-aids-embattled-004344471.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref name="Law Enforcement Concerns and Engagement">{{cite web | url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-pokemon-go-police-fire-20160715-snap-story.html | title='You may NOT access our jail': Police and fire official air grievances over 'Pokemon Go' | publisher=Los Angeles Times | date=2016-07-16 | accessdate=2016-07-16 | author=Rocha, Veronica | archive-date=2016-07-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715234933/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-pokemon-go-police-fire-20160715-snap-story.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 商家則因鄰近寶可夢基站帶來的人潮受益（商家甚至本身就是寶可補給站）。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-07-11/pok-mon-go-brings-real-money-to-random-bars-and-pizzerias |title = Pokémon Go Brings Real Money to Random Bars and Pizzerias |website = Bloomberg |access-date = 2016-07-14 |archive-date = 2016-07-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160713212022/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-07-11/pok-mon-go-brings-real-money-to-random-bars-and-pizzerias |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1 = Shields |first1 = Mike |last2 = Perlberg |first2 = Steven |title = Ad Agencies Scramble to Form ‘Pokémon Go’ Strategies |url = http://www.wsj.com/articles/ad-agencies-scramble-to-form-pokemon-go-strategies-1468425523 |accessdate = 2016-07-14 |work = Wall Street Journal |date = 2016-07-13 |archive-date = 2016-07-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160713171605/http://www.wsj.com/articles/ad-agencies-scramble-to-form-pokemon-go-strategies-1468425523 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1 = Shaw |first1 = Sydney |title = How N.J. businesses are benefiting from Pokémon Go craze |url = http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2016/07/pokemon_go_might_be_restaurants_and_retailers_new.html |accessdate = 2016-07-14 |date = 2016-07-14 |archive-date = 2016-07-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160716204124/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2016/07/pokemon_go_might_be_restaurants_and_retailers_new.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

由於遊戲設定將不少宝可梦的補給點，放置在社區地標、公園、歷史建築、甚至在電信公司在彩繪變電箱上。因此手機遊戲開放下載後，讓過往不多關心社區身邊事物的民眾，除了可以多作運動之外，也可以重新認識自己居住的區域。

以[[香港|香港]]為例，不少公園大多時間只有老人家享用。但遊戲上市後，陸續多了不少年輕人在公園漫步和聚集。<ref>{{cite news|title= 【Pokemon GO】海心公園伯伯：從未見過公園咁多年輕人|url= http://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80/33722/-Pokemon-GO-%E6%B5%B7%E5%BF%83%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E4%BC%AF%E4%BC%AF-%E5%BE%9E%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%8B%E9%81%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E5%92%81%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA|accessdate= 2016-07-26|agency= [[香港01|香港01]]|location= 香港|author= 麥佩雯|date= 2016-07-26|archive-date= 2017-03-05|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170305002940/http://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80/33722/-Pokemon-GO-%E6%B5%B7%E5%BF%83%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E4%BC%AF%E4%BC%AF-%E5%BE%9E%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%8B%E9%81%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E5%92%81%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA|dead-url= no}}</ref>其中在平日被「[[大媽|大媽]]」佔據的[[天水圍|天水圍]][[天秀路公園|天秀路公園]]，到晚上有多達千人进行游戏，人群至深夜11、12時仍未散去。<ref>{{cite news |title=【Pokémon Go殺到】訓練員趕走大媽 天水圍公園深夜千人鍛鍊 |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160726/55413473 |language=中文 |publisher=蘋果日報 |date=2016-07-26 |accessdate=2016-07-27 |archive-date=2016-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160727133009/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160726/55413473 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
而且，一些行駛速度較慢的公共交通工具如[[香港電車|電車]]、[[九龍巴士53線|九龍巴士53線]]等等都因能方便玩家安坐的同時能捕捉宝可梦而客量突然上升 <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/m/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1oyBw5ZHwNr |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-08-13 |archive-date=2016-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822190047/http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/m/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1oyBw5ZHwNr |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.weekendhk.com/lifestyle/pokemon-go-%e5%b7%b4%e5%a3%ab%e7%b7%9a-%e7%b2%be%e9%9d%88%e8%a8%93%e7%b7%b4%e5%93%a1/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-08-13 |archive-date=2016-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821144456/http://www.weekendhk.com/lifestyle/pokemon-go-%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E7%B7%9A-%E7%B2%BE%E9%9D%88%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E5%93%A1/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，其中[[九龍巴士1A線|九龍巴士1A線]]更加密班次，甚至設有後備車，某程度上亦舒緩了[[港鐵|港鐵]]的擠逼情況。

